      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's all gone. the last ten years... all those papers, the grants, the theories... they were all based on a fundamental error i just realized. i've spent my whole life building a monument to a lie. i look in the mirror and i don't even see a person, just a fraud. there's nothing left for me here.",
