    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"starting fresh\" thing... it's just a platitude. You don't get it. It's not like I lost a job or a relationship. I lost the foundation of my entire reality. The work was my identity. Without the truth of those theories, there is no \"me\" to start over. I'm just an empty shell that wasted a decade on nothing. It feels like the universe is just correcting a mistake, and I'm the mistake.",
